\begin_layout Section
Know Thyself
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
As the form factor of our computational devices gets increasingly personal
 -- smartphones and smartwatches are quickly becoming ubiquitous and are
 with us all the time -- it is important to reflect on the effect they have
 in our lives.
 For the most part, they are greatly beneficial as they allow us to stay
 connected with loved ones, access to a wealth of information, work, play,
 etc.
 However, this constant ability to be connected -- or inability of being
 alone 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "turkle2012alone"

\end_inset

 -- leaves little time for our minds for calmness and contemplation.
 Email is operating 24h a day while we clearly cannot.
 While calmness and contemplation might appear to be important only for
 an overall feeling of well-being -- which is very important on its own
 --, it is also central in fostering creativity and innovation.
 In his book 
