 and mental processes.
 Chapter 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "cha:teegi"

\end_inset

 present a friendly little character named Teegi -- Tangible Electroncephalograp
hy (EEG) Interface -- a tangible interface to learn more about the internal
 working of the brain.
 EEG is a technology that measures the electric current 
